WMSTime

public WMSTime(String theTimeStr)
        throws RIMapperException
constructor: Analyses and picks aparts a TIME (ISO8601:1988(E)) parameter. Deals with single time instance ( 'datetime' ) OR contiguous time periods ( 'datetime_begin/datetime_end' ) Ignores periodicity for now: ('datetime_begin/datetime_end/Period') => last part is ignored and contiguous time period is returned
